<div class="container w-50">
  <div class="feedback-heading">
    <h1 class="heading">Feedback</h1>
    <h3 class="heading">Your results are in...</h3>

    <h4 class="heading">You have recorded having a BM of <%= @reading %></h4>

  <div class="reading">
  <% if @reading > 4 %>
    <p>Your value is a bit on the high side. Here are some recipes we'd like to recommend, based on your BM input.
  <% elsif @reading >= 2 && @reading <= 4 %>
    <p>Your value is normal! Well done Mama! Keep up the good work. If you want to have a look at some recipes, here are some that could inspire you!
  <% elsif @reading < 2 %>
    <p>Your value is a bit on the low side. Here are some recipes we'd like to recommend, based on your BM input.
  <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class="buttons-container">
      <%= link_to "Recipes", meals_path, class: "button" %>
    </div>
   </div>

  <div class="meal-index-card">
    <h1>Meal Feedback</h1>



    <div class="meal-cards-container">
      <% Meal.all.group_by(&:timing).transform_values(&:first).values.each do |meal| %>
        <div class="meal-card">
          <div class="meal-image">
            <a href="<%= meals_path%>">
            <%= image_tag meal.image, alt: meal.name %>

            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="meal-name">
            <p><%= meal.name %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>


  </div>

</div>
